import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Math from './Math'

function Categories() {
  return (
    <>
    <Nav fill variant="tabs" defaultActiveKey="/home">
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link href="/Math" element={<Math />}>Math</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="/Math" element={<Math />}>Loooonger NavLink</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">Link</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="disabled" disabled>
          Disabled
        </Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
    </Nav>
    </>


  );
}

export default Categories;
